\f0\b\fs26 \cf0 \ul \ulc0 THE HELIOPTICON
\f1\b0\fs24 \ulnone \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs26 \cf0 \
This is the formal collective name of the governmental and cultural institutions who control the Fatunik regions of the Saskan Lands.  It is also referred to as \'93The Fatunik Union\'94, although strictly speaking that is the name of the collective body of representatives of the various Fatunik Guilds, whereas the geo-political entity they control is \'93The Fatunika\'94.
\fs24 \

\fs26 \
 
\fs24 \

\fs26 It is not incorrect to characterize the Fatunika as an aspiring but not entirely successful theological-military dictatorship with important populist tendencies.  Its power is far from absolute.  Nor is its role and influence entirely dire. 
\fs24 \

\fs26 \
They really do protect the population \'96 especially the huum population, but also others under their protections \'96 of Saskantinon from external and internal threats.  Its Central Power, called the Heliocastron, rules over a relatively prosperous and secure region that is surrounded by threats. During tumultuous times, the Heliocastronic Center is perceived by many as a source of stability and protection.
\fs24 \

\fs26 \
\
Residents of the Fatunika who follow the Fatunik belief system are referred to as Heliops.  Anyone who resides or travels through the Fatunika is subject to its laws.
\fs24 \

\fs26 \
There are 10 loyal Fatunik provinces.\
